17:30.516 --> 17:38.925 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Now to Iraq, and
an exclusive
look at the Iraqi city of
Fallujah, from the

17:38.958 --> 17:43.729 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
