still large
pockets of ISIS fighters.

19:39.378 --> 19:43.182 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's also clear that, even
though the city
has been spared a lot of the
destruction of

19:43.215 --> 19:50.456 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Ramadi, the provincial capital,
