civilian we see
is Bushra Daud. There hasn't
been electricity

20:03.602 --> 20:08.641 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
or running water here for months
and there's
hardly any food. She can't
explain why she

20:08.674 --> 20:10.376 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
stayed.

20:10.409 --> 20:16.615 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ISIS controlled Fallujah for two
years, running
a city of almost 100,000 people.
"We wage

20:16.649 --> 20:21.887 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
