Allah," they
wrote in this public square.

20:21.921 --> 20:27.426 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Fighter Ali Sami Hadi tells us
the bridge
above is now dedicated to a
wounded Iraqi

20:27.460 --> 20:29.328 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
