20:29.361 --> 20:32.698 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ALI SAMI HADI, Iraq (through
translator):
ISIS slaughtered those who
opposed them or

20:32.731 --> 20:37.136 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
