20:55.154 --> 21:00.726 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HAIDER AL-ABADI, Iraqi Prime
Minister: This
was quite a challenge, but we
were prepared

21:00.759 --> 21:06.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
