21:47.306 --> 21:53.946 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JANE ARRAF: Nearby, a commander
of the mostly
Shia paramilitary forces is
mobbed by supporters.

21:53.979 --> 22:01.253 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
