be kept out
of the much bigger fight ahead
in Mosul.

22:06.292 --> 22:11.297 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ABU MAHDI AL-MUHANDIS, Iraq
(through translator):
We gave thousands of martyrs as
casualties

22:11.330 --> 22:15.901 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
