22:17.736 --> 22:21.840 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JANE ARRAF: It's an important
victory for
the Iraqi government and an
important step

22:21.874 --> 22:27.980 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
