brought me from
Baghdad to here, and I don't
know why.

23:20.766 --> 23:25.104 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JANE ARRAF: Day after day in
desolate camps
in the desert, families wait for
news of their

23:25.137 --> 23:31.410 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
