here. There isn't even enough
water or toilets.

23:47.559 --> 23:52.931 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And there are few aid
organizations. U.N.
officials say the U.S. is
focusing on the

23:52.965 --> 23:58.637 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
