while underfunding
humanitarian aid.

23:58.671 --> 24:04.743 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The Norwegian Refugee Council,
the NRC, is
one of the few international
organizations

24:04.777 --> 24:07.246 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
here.

24:07.279 --> 24:10.182 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Regional director Carsten Hansen
says it's
a catastrophe.

24:10.215 --> 24:14.687 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CARSTEN HANSEN, Norwegian
Refugee Council:
Horrible. So, for us, it's --
first of all,

24:14.720 --> 24:21.026 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
we would like and we are
appealing to our
colleagues in the NGO community
and the U.N.,

24:21.060 --> 24:22.961 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
we need to scale up.

24:22.995 --> 24:27.900 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JANE ARRAF: On this day, they
