46:30.054 --> 46:31.856 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
LESLEY M.M. BLUME: Exactly.

46:31.889 --> 46:36.260 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And it turned out that she --
her name was
Lady Duff Twysden, and she was
