46:57.982 --> 46:59.650 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
LESLEY M.M. BLUME: I wrote it.

46:59.684 --> 47:02.353 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Remind us about
"The Sun Also
Rises," the story, the novel
