47:02.386 --> 47:08.626 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LESLEY M.M. BLUME: It came out
in 1926, and
it is a group of American and
British expats

47:08.659 --> 47:13.364 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
