all there to be writers or
artists.

47:17.268 --> 47:23.240 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
In the case of Lady Duff
Twysden, she was
there to sit out an aristocratic
divorce.

47:23.274 --> 47:31.148 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
