say, dissolves
into quite a brouhaha.

47:37.722 --> 47:39.957 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Yes, all kinds of
shenanigans.

47:39.990 --> 47:42.093 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
LESLEY M.M. BLUME: Yes, a lot of
bad behavior.

47:42.126 --> 47:44.995 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Yes. Rivalries,
