had written.

48:18.362 --> 48:21.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
LESLEY M.M. BLUME: Well,
Hemingway at that
time up to that point and after
the fact was

48:21.899 --> 48:25.236 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
