being a really
good reporter.

48:25.269 --> 48:29.640 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And one of the real-life
inspirations behind
"The Sun Also Rises" characters
literally

48:29.673 --> 48:34.111 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
