there to stage
his breakthrough. So many of the
expats who

48:53.631 --> 49:00.171 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
were there at that time were
there to do precisely
that. It was an ambition-fueled
town.

49:00.204 --> 49:04.842 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Hemingway was looking to make a
big splash
with a revolutionary new modern
style that

49:04.875 --> 49:09.814 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
