just really got
to the point. There was quite a
journalistic

49:09.847 --> 49:14.318 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
element to that style also. He
wasn't the
only person in town doing it,
but he was the

49:14.351 --> 49:17.488 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
one who knew that he could do it
in a commercially
successful way.

49:17.521 --> 49:22.259 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Not only was he
the only person
in town, but a lot of famous
people in town,

49:22.293 --> 49:25.429 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
