Stein and Ezra
Pound.

49:25.462 --> 49:29.900 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LESLEY M.M. BLUME: All three of
those people
really helped Hemingway
significantly, and

49:29.934 --> 49:34.071 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
