mentors to Hemingway.

49:34.104 --> 49:38.576 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But they weren't selling a lot
of copies of
their work. Gertrude Stein
famously only sold

49:38.609 --> 49:43.647 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
